query:
DELETE FROM cycles 
WHERE id IN (
  SELECT c.id FROM (
    SELECT cycles.id
    FROM cycles
    LEFT JOIN goals ON goals.cycleId = cycles.id
    WHERE goals.id IS NULL
      AND (cycles.title LIKE '%Test%' OR cycles.title LIKE '%Bulk%')
  ) c
)
